sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Ad Click Source
    participant Stream as Event Stream (by ad_id)
    participant Streamer as Stream Processor
    participant OLAP as OLAP Store
    participant Lake as Object Store (raw)
    participant Batch as Batch Processor
    participant Billing as Billing System

    Note over Client,Stream: Ingest
    Client->>Stream: POST /click (ad_id, user, ts, ip)
    Stream->>Stream: Append to ad_id partition

    Note over Stream,OLAP: Real-time path (5-min freshness)
    Streamer->>Stream: Read partition (transactional)
    Streamer->>Streamer: keyBy(ad_id), tumbling 1-min window
    alt Late event within allowed lateness
        Streamer->>Streamer: Update past bucket
    else Outside lateness
        Streamer->>Streamer: Side output (drop from main agg)
    end
    Streamer->>Streamer: Checkpoint state + offsets atomically
    Streamer->>OLAP: Write (ad_id, ts_minute, count) idempotent

    Note over Stream,Lake: Batch path (authoritative)
    Stream-)Lake: Tee raw events to Parquet
    loop Nightly
        Batch->>Lake: Read full day raw events
        Batch->>Batch: Recompute aggregates
        Batch->>OLAP: Reconcile vs streaming output
        Batch->>Billing: Authoritative daily totals
    end
